        "title":"",
        "phase": '<p><b>Secondary cold agglutinin disease</b> is associated with:</p><p>Lymphomas: CLL, Waldenström macroglobulinemia, angioimmunoblastic T-cell lymphoma Multiple myeloma</p><p>Kaposi sarcoma</p><p>Carcinomas: lung squamous cell, metastatic adrenal, metastatic colon, mixed parotid tumor, and basal cell</p><div class="suggested_readings"><p>Suggested Readings:</p><p>Greer JP, Arber DA, Glader BE, List AF, Means RT Jr, Rodgers GM. <em>Wintrobe’s Clinical Hematology</em>. 14th ed. Wolters Kluwer; 2018.</p><p>Kaushansky K, Prchal JT, Burns LJ, Lichtman MA, Levi M, Linch DC. <em>Williams Hematology</em>. 10th ed. McGraw Hill; 2021.</p></div>'
